T02TD1936E:64b-1: krishna ya m'a ri s'a dha nam n'a ma /
T02TD1936E:64b-3: gshin rje gshed nag po'i sgrub thabs zhes bya ba /
T02TD1936E:64b-4: dpal rdo rje sems dpa' la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD1936E:64b-5: rje btsun rdo rje sems bdag sngags //
T02TD1936E:64b-6: 'jigs byed dpa' bo dgra nag la //
T02TD1936E:64b-7: btud de brgyud rim las rnyed pa //
T02TD1936E:64b-8: dngos grub 'byung phyir bshad par bya //
T02TD1936E:64b-9: rang gzugs rdzogs pa'i snying ga ru //
T02TD1936E:64b-10: ya yig las ni 'gro bar sbyang //
T02TD1936E:64b-11: bdun po yis kyang sbyang byas nas //
T02TD1936E:64b-12: tshangs pa'i gnas la gzhag par bya //
T02TD1936E:64b-13: stong pa'i snying po gsal bar bsam //
T02TD1936E:64b-14: bsrung ba padmar ldan pa'i nang //
T02TD1936E:64b-15: chu skyes ri bong can rnon po //
T02TD1936E:64b-16: byang chub rgyu yi gshin rje gshed //
T02TD1936E:64b-17: rtsa ba'i zhal gyi khyad par can //
T02TD1936E:64b-18: zhu ba'i thig le gyi yon tan bsam byas nas //
T02TD1936E:64b-19: bsod nams rgya cher rab tu bzlog pa brgyad kyis sku brgyan cing //
T02TD1936E:64b-20: rus pas brgyan cing dum bus dpal gshin rje bshed //
T02TD1936E:65a-2: g-yas dang g-yon pa dkar dang dmar //
T02TD1936E:65a-3: phag mo de mtshungs dam 'khyud pa //
T02TD1936E:65a-4: gri gug thod pa rtsa ba'i phyag / rdo rje bar dang tha ma gri //
T02TD1936E:65a-6: thod pa lnga yi dbu rgyan can //
T02TD1936E:65a-7: ser brdzes spyan dgu bzlog cing 'gyur //
T02TD1936E:65a-8: lnga bcu'i do shal mnyam du dpyangs //
T02TD1936E:65a-9: gdug pa brgyad kyis sku brgyan cing //
T02TD1936E:65a-10: rus pas brgyan cing dum bus sgeg / mtshon cha bcu gnyis 'khrug par bsam //
T02TD1936E:65a-11: ma he la bzhugs srid rtser 'bar //
T02TD1936E:65a-12: sku gsung thugs dang skye mched dang //
T02TD1936E:65a-13: dbang dang byin rlabs mchod dang bstod //
T02TD1936E:65a-14: bdud rtsi myong dang spro bsdu dang //
T02TD1936E:65a-15: bzlas pa'i rim pa'i man ngag las //
T02TD1936E:65a-17: aom k'a la r'u pa h'um /
T02TD1936E:65a-26: h'um h'um phat phat sv'a h'a /
T02TD1936E:65a-27: aom hr'i: shtri: wi kri t'a na na h'um h'um phat phat sv'a h'a /
T02TD1936E:65a-28: drug pas gtor ma bsnyen par bya //
T02TD1936E:65a-29: sum cu brgyad pas nye bar bsnyen //
T02TD1936E:65a-30: bco lnga pas ni thams cad bsgrub //
T02TD1936E:65a-31: las kyi 'khor lo bskor bar bya //
T02TD1936E:65a-32: gshed nag rgyud dang 'byung ba las //
T02TD1936E:65a-33: rnyed de sgrub thabs 'di bris pas //
T02TD1936E:65a-34: blo ni rab dag gyur nas kyang //
T02TD1936E:65a-35: gshin rje gshed du 'gyur bar shog / gshin rje gshed nag po'i sgrub thabs /
T02TD1936E:65a-36: slob dpon mkhas pa chen po dpal mar me mdzad kyis mdzad pa rdzogs so /
T02TD1936E:65a-38: // / rnal 'byor pa pradzny'a shr'i dzny'a na k'irtis rang 'gyur du mdzad do//
